headline: Robinhood, Maker Of Popular Trading App, Succeeds In Opposing Trademark Application For "Robin Hood" In Canada
summary: On 24 March 2025, the Trademarks Opposition Board refused a trademark application for the mark Robin Hood because it was considered confusing with the previously registered trademark ROBINHOOD owned...
